angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da03dab6a9fe2e9bc5a7d76bcf98fdddfe499b64","tid":7030,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4e841197b478b6b9a983bc8604557a60afd628","tid":7030,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"依家 <br />\n番full time學+3份pt(3份唔同行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n不過我知好碎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大把人難捱過我"},{"pid":"e31303ac9794da0835439168c830fc654fed0528","tid":7030,"uid":11662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為責任<br />\n唔係仲有責任在身 放棄咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n努力地等緊責任完成嘅一日，我就可以解脫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb793fbe9a1a22a859b7582c1cf47f4cf23b6d2e","tid":7030,"uid":14932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"時間同自我安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然好罕 但一日一日咁過真係會過到 跟住就會有新嘅開始 新嘅考驗 就算重新遇到難捱嘅日子 會因為有經歷而知道時間會慢慢沖淡一切～雖然過程好辛苦 但諗番會覺得自己原來不知不覺咁捱過咗 當然身邊嘅人都好重要 朋友同屋企人支持住  但如果黎啲都冇嘅時候 我會同自己講仲有我自己 當我仲係到嘅時候就已經唔係失去所有 當你有經歷就會知 無論依家幾難過都好 冇嘢會過唔去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fa162d3b36c54dbcfba3a1de66d34b44ede5cf","tid":7030,"uid":17224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:34:46.000Z","msg":"每晚瞓之前都諗自己會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c9427988c175e466dd4d3a3f8b83e9362ef69a","tid":7030,"uid":19989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"同返因為拍拖而冷落咗嘅朋友聯絡 然後又折墮咁去識吓其他異性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實要放低一個人最好就係搵第二個人代替佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 好愛現任"},{"pid":"033a8f015b1c7b580473a39fbaa6360aa40d0ce9","tid":7030,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間同自我安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然好罕 但一日一日咁過真係會過到 跟住就會有新嘅開始 新嘅考驗 就算重新遇到難捱嘅日子 會因為有經歷而知道時間會慢慢沖淡一切～雖然過程好辛苦 但諗番會覺得自己原來不知不覺咁捱過咗 當然身邊嘅人都好重要 朋友同屋企人支持住  但如果黎啲都冇嘅時候 我會同自己講仲有我自己 當我仲係到嘅時候就已經唔係失去所有 當你有經歷就會知 無論依家幾難過都好 冇嘢會過唔去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講係咁講，但有時連自己都否定自己時就唔係咁講，情緒低落時自殺諗頭隨之而現，樂觀既人未必明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af63eef5cd15dc2a17716e21585d70b7f31f7e40","tid":7030,"uid":11662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:47:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>時間同自我安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然好罕 但一日一日咁過真係會過到 跟住就會有新嘅開始 新嘅考驗 就算重新遇到難捱嘅日子 會因為有經歷而知道時間會慢慢沖淡一切～雖然過程好辛苦 但諗番會覺得自己原來不知不覺咁捱過咗 當然身邊嘅人都好重要 朋友同屋企人支持住  但如果黎啲都冇嘅時候 我會同自己講仲有我自己 當我仲係到嘅時候就已經唔係失去所有 當你有經歷就會知 無論依家幾難過都好 冇嘢會過唔去 <img src=\"/as